255
00:16:13,291 --> 00:16:14,333
- Hei, Maddie.
- Bagus.

256
00:16:14,416 --> 00:16:16,125
- Sean. Ayah Paul.
- Hai.

257
00:16:17,041 --> 00:16:18,041
Tidak!

