00:16:31,291 --> 00:16:32,208
Tak apa-apa.

263
00:16:32,291 --> 00:16:33,416
Itu diasuransikan.

264
00:16:33,500 --> 00:16:36,791
Bukan kopernya yang kami cemaskan,
