1111
01:13:26,208 --> 01:13:28,000
- Ada apa ini?
- Astaga.

1112
01:13:28,583 --> 01:13:31,416
Dia memakai apa?
Di mana gaun pengantin keluarga?

1113
01:13:40,500 --> 01:13:41,458
Hai.

1114
01:13:43,041 --> 01:13:45,500
Bagi yang tak mengenalku, aku Maddie,

1115
01:13:46,208 --> 01:13:47,208
