1116
01:13:47,791 --> 01:13:49,875
Setidaknya, seharusnya begitu.

1117
01:13:51,000 --> 01:13:52,875
Tentu saja, kalian kenal Paul.

1118
01:13:53,583 --> 01:13:56,666
